<div class="report-info">
<p>The City Highways Division maintains Stamford's over 315 miles of centerline road, which is the largest municipal road system in the State.</p>
<p>Crews located at four facilities throughout Stamford handle all the maintenance and repair activities, including but not limited to storm system cleaning, road maintenance, snow plowing, and leaf pickup.</p>
<p>The Highway team is dedicated to maintaining the wellness of the traveling public as well as the safety and aesthetic value of the infrastructure.</p>
